Reasoning: The paper uses Google Street View images and manual annotation to predict travel patterns at the city level, which involves computer vision techniques and image analysis (cs.CV). It also involves statistical modeling and regression analysis (cs.SI). The study focuses on urban mobility and transportation planning (cs.CY), and uses big data sources (cs.CE) to make predictions. Finally, the paper discusses the potential of using street imagery for cross-sectional and longitudinal assessments, which may involve issues related to privacy and ethics (cs.CR).
